<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    @page { margin: 12mm 10mm; }
    :root {
      --ocean-blue: #204050;
      --tropical-green: #3d6b54;
      --sand-beige: #f0e0e0;
      --sunset-gold: #c08020;
      --paper: #f0f0f0;
      --ink: #1f2933;
      --muted: #687283;
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Mundial', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: var(--ink); font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.5; background: var(--paper); }
    .page { border: 1px solid #dde2ea; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; background: #f5f6f8; }
    .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--ocean-blue); padding-bottom: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .logo { font-family: 'Alegros', Georgia, serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ocean-blue); }
    .logo span { color: var(--sunset-gold); }
    .header h1 { font-family: 'Alegros', Georgia, serif; font-size: 24px; color: var(--ocean-blue); margin-top: 6px; }
    .header .subtitle { color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }
    .welcome { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #204050, #3d6b54); color: #fff; padding: 14px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .welcome h2 { font-family: 'Alegros', Georgia, serif; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .pillar { border: 1px solid #d8dde6; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .pillar h3 { font-family: 'Alegros', Georgia, serif; background: #f3f6f9; color: var(--ocean-blue); padding: 9px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #d8dde6; }
    .pillar-body { padding: 10px 12px; }
    .day-card { border: 1px solid #d8dde6; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .day-header { background: var(--ocean-blue); color: white; padding: 9px 12px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; }
    .day-body { padding: 12px; }
    .day-body .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .detail { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .detail .label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .detail .value { font-weight: 600; color: #111827; }
    .notes-section { background: #f7f0e3; border-left: 4px solid var(--sunset-gold); padding: 11px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 10px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .notes-section h3 { font-family: 'Alegros', Georgia, serif; font-size: 15px; color: var(--ocean-blue); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .cta-list { margin-top: 14px; list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
    .cta-list li {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      padding-left: 28px;
      color: #3f4d61;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .cta-list li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .cta-list li::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0.56em;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #42546b;
    }
    .footer { margin-top: 16px; text-align: center; padding: 12px; background: #f4f6f8; border: 1px solid #d8dde6; border-radius: 10px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    .footer p { color: #5f6875; font-size: 13px; }
    .footer .brand { font-family: 'Alegros', Georgia, serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ocean-blue); margin-bottom: 4px; }

    /* Safe adaptive mode: mild compaction for denser itineraries */
    body.compact { font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.42; }
    body.compact .page { padding: 14px; }
    body.compact .header { padding-bottom: 11px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    body.compact .logo { font-size: 27px; }
    body.compact .header h1 { font-size: 22px; }
    body.compact .welcome { padding: 11px; margin-bottom: 11px; }
    body.compact .welcome h2 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    body.compact .pillar { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    body.compact .pillar h3 { padding: 8px 10px; }
    body.compact .pillar-body { padding: 8px 10px; }
    body.compact .day-card { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    body.compact .day-header { padding: 8px 10px; font-size: 14px; }
    body.compact .day-body { padding: 10px; }
    body.compact .day-body .grid { gap: 10px; }
    body.compact .detail { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    body.compact .notes-section { padding: 9px; margin-top: 8px; }
    body.compact .notes-section h3 { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    body.compact .footer { margin-top: 12px; padding: 10px; }
    body.compact .cta-list { margin-top: 10px; }
    body.compact .cta-list li { margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 13px; }
    body.compact .cta-list li::before { width: 7px; height: 7px; top: 0.6em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="{{layoutMode}}">
  <div class="page">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">VSL <span>360</span></div>
    <h1>Itinerary Story</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Experience Sri Lanka Completely</p>
  </div>

  <div class="welcome">
    <h2>Dear {{client.name}},</h2>
    <p>Welcome to a {{booking.numberOfDays}}-day journey shaped with local character, thoughtful comfort, and meaningful moments.</p>
    <p>{{formatDate booking.arrivalDate}} - {{formatDate booking.departureDate}}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar">
    <h3>Destination Discovery</h3>
    <div class="pillar-body">
      Your route has been curated to balance iconic scenery with quieter corners of Sri Lanka, creating a complete sense of place from arrival to departure.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pillar">
    <h3>Travel Experiences</h3>
    <div class="pillar-body">
      Each transfer and activity is arranged to keep your days seamless, so you can focus on the experience itself rather than the logistics.
    </div>
  </div>

  {{#if transport}}
  <div class="day-card">
    <div class="day-header">Arrival Details</div>
    <div class="day-body">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Pickup Location</span><div class="value">{{transport.arrivalPickupLocation}}</div></div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Pickup Time</span><div class="value">{{transport.arrivalPickupTime}}</div></div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Vehicle</span><div class="value">{{transport.vehicleModel}}</div></div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Driver</span><div class="value">{{transport.driverName}} ({{transport.driverLanguage}})</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{#each days}}
  <div class="day-card">
    <div class="day-header">Day {{this.dayNumber}}</div>
    <div class="day-body">
      <div class="grid">
        {{#if this.hotel}}
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Hotel</span><div class="value">{{this.hotel.hotelName}}</div></div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Room</span><div class="value">{{this.hotel.roomCategory}}</div></div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Meal Plan</span><div class="value">{{this.hotel.mealPlan}}</div></div>
        {{#if this.hotel.mealPreference}}
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Meal Preference</span><div class="value">{{this.hotel.mealPreference}}</div></div>
        {{/if}}
        {{/if}}
        {{#if this.transport}}
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Activities</span><div class="value">{{this.transport.description}}</div></div>
        {{#if this.transport.pickupTime}}
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Pickup</span><div class="value">{{this.transport.pickupTime}} — {{this.transport.pickupLocation}}</div></div>
        {{/if}}
        {{/if}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/each}}

  <div class="pillar">
    <h3>Luxury Stays</h3>
    <div class="pillar-body">
      Your stays are selected for comfort, atmosphere, and location, so each evening feels like part of the journey, not just a stop between destinations.
    </div>
  </div>

  {{#if transport}}
  <div class="day-card">
    <div class="day-header">Departure Details</div>
    <div class="day-body">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Drop-off Location</span><div class="value">{{transport.departureDropLocation}}</div></div>
        <div class="detail"><span class="label">Drop-off Time</span><div class="value">{{transport.departureDropTime}}</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{#if booking.generalNotes}}
  <div class="notes-section">
    <h3>Important Notes</h3>
    <p>{{booking.generalNotes}}</p>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  {{#if booking.specialCelebrations}}
  <div class="notes-section" style="margin-top: 12px;">
    <h3>Local Culture & Celebrations</h3>
    <p>{{booking.specialCelebrations}}</p>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  <div class="pillar">
    <h3>Travel Moments</h3>
    <div class="pillar-body">
      Look out for candid moments in warm natural light: sunrise roads, tea-country air, coastal evenings, and conversations that make the island memorable.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="brand">VSL 360</div>
    <p>Curated Travel Experiences</p>
    <ul class="cta-list">
      <li>When you are ready, we would be delighted to design your next Sri Lankan chapter.</li>
      <li>Share your preferred dates, and we will craft another journey around your travel style.</li>
      <li>Let us know the moments you value most, and we will shape the itinerary around them.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
